0.0.1.name: wordpress/tiga
0.0.1.description: Responsive, clean and elegant theme, perfect for bloggers or even professionals. It supports 5 widget areas, 4 custom widgets(facebook like box, subscribe, social and twitter), 10 custom background patterns and social share buttons, Search engine friendly, cross browser also translation ready. It has an optional twentytwelve like custom home page template, full-width page template, sitemap page template, blog page with slider page, one-column & two-columns flexible-width layouts. It include plug-and-play support for the WP-Pagenavi plugin. Another amazing features is bbPress & BuddyPress support! Get support here http://satrya.me/forums
